happy international women‚Äôs day! üíú

this marks my 4th year officially being a woman in crypto and I could not be more proud to be one alongside so many inspirational ladies each and every day.

i went to an all girls middle school, which left me thinking that women always had to be pitted against each other. this could not be further from the truth.

empowered women empower women.
they say your name in a room full of opportunities.
and they want nothing more than to celebrate your successes.

i know now that i am in good company. 

so here‚Äôs to another year of improving the gender ratio at both crypto conferences and on our timeline ü•Ç
